---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="SOC 2 readiness and audit support for technology companies. Get audit-ready with confidence.">
  <HeroSection
    headline="SOC 2 Readiness for Technology Companies"
    subheadline="Close enterprise deals faster. Reduce procurement friction. Get audit-ready with confidence."
    ctaText="Get Started"
    ctaHref="/about"
  />

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>Why SOC 2 Matters</h2>
    <p>Enterprise buyers require SOC 2 before signing procurement contracts. Without it, your sales cycle stalls, deals slip, and competitors with compliance credentials win the business.</p>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Unlock Enterprise Sales</h3>
        <p>SOC 2 is the baseline requirement for B2B SaaS, AI, data, and developer-tooling companies selling to enterprise customers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Demonstrate Security Posture</h3>
        <p>A SOC 2 report proves to customers and partners that your organization takes security seriously and operates with mature controls.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Reduce Procurement Friction</h3>
        <p>Skip the lengthy security questionnaires. A SOC 2 report answers the questions enterprise procurement teams are already asking.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Accelerate Trust</h3>
        <p>Prospects evaluate your security posture before they evaluate your product. SOC 2 readiness shortens the trust-building process.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>How We Help</h2>
    <p>Four service packages designed to meet you where you are in your compliance journey.</p>
    <div class="service-overview-grid">
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Readiness Sprint</h3>
        <p>Scope, assess, and plan in 2&#8211;4 weeks</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Remediation Program</h3>
        <p>Close gaps and build your evidence machine</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Audit Support</h3>
        <p>Expert coordination during audit fieldwork</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Continuous Compliance</h3>
        <p>Stay audit-ready year-round</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p>Whether you're pursuing SOC 2 for the first time or need help maintaining compliance, we can help you build a readiness plan that fits your team and timeline.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-button">Let's Talk</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .service-overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card {
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .service-overview-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-heading);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem var(--spacing-page);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
